## I moved to a different world!

![GitHub Logo](http://jaroca.co/assets/images/logo-600-170.png)

I really did move to a different world. Now I work on what has been my family business since 1975, founded by my grandfather, now managed by 3 cousins and myself. It is an architectural solutions in wood, aluminium and PVC factory.

**Changed servers for saws!**

[Jaroca SAS](http://jaroca.co)

That means this blog enters a never-ending sleep.
